-ING TAKISI ILE BAGLANACAK FIILLER:
like, enjoy, dislike, love, hate, regret
I like eating ice cream.

-TO TAKISI ILE BAGLANACAK FIILLER:
want, plan, need, hope, fail
I want to eat ice cream.

